casebody.data:
No. 777,

Misc.

Fontana v. Schneckloth, Warden, et al. Petitioner pro se. Thomas C. Lynch, Attorney General of California, and Edsel W. Haws and Roger E. Venturi, Deputy Attorneys General, for respondents.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari is denied.
